Type of links and email addresses must be a resource (IRI), not a literal

 
# Type of links and email addresses must be a resource (IRI), not a literal

PREFIX dcat:    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#>
PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
PREFIX foaf:    <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>
PREFIX vcard:   <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#>

SELECT ?subject ?property ?value
WHERE {
    ?subject ?property ?value
    FILTER (!isIRI(?value))
    VALUES ?property {
        dcat:accessURL
        dcat:downloadURL
        dcat:landingPage
        foaf:homepage
        foaf:page
        vcard:hasEmail
    }
}

Not using EU Publication Office Authority

 
# Not using EU Publication Office Authority

PREFIX dcat:    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#>
PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>

SELECT ?subject ?property
WHERE {
    ?subject ?property ?obj
    FILTER NOT EXISTS {
        ?subject ?property ?value
        FILTER (isIRI(?value) && STRSTARTS(STR(?value), ?taxonomy))
    }
    VALUES (?property ?taxonomy) {
        (dcat:theme         "http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/")
        (dcterms:format     "http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/file-type/")
        (dcterms:language   "http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/")
        (dcterms:accrualPeriodicity "http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/")
    }
}

Dataset missing publisher

 
# Dataset missing publisher

PREFIX dcat:    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#>
PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>

SELECT ?dataset
WHERE {
    ?dataset a dcat:Dataset
    FILTER NOT EXISTS { 
        ?dataset dcterms:publisher ?value
    }
}

OK

Duplicate identifier

 
# Duplicate identifier

PREFIX dcat:    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#>
PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>

SELECT ?dataset
WHERE {
    ?dataset dcterms:identifier ?value .
    ?dataset2 dcterms:identifier ?value
    FILTER (?dataset != ?dataset2)
}

OK

# Contactpoint missing email

PREFIX vcard:   <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#>

SELECT ?org
WHERE {
    ?org a vcard:Organization
    FILTER NOT EXISTS { 
        ?org vcard:hasEmail ?email
    }
}

Missing language tag

 
# Missing language tag

PREFIX dcat:    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#>
PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>

SELECT ?subject ?property ?value
WHERE {
    ?subject ?property ?value
    FILTER (isLiteral(?value) && lang(?value) = "" )
    VALUES ?property {
        dcterms:title
        dcterms:description
        dcterms:keyword
    }
}
